divs: Sighting Details I was sitting under my car port and I always look out at the Big clouds passing by. It is a hooby that I do to pass the time before I eat supper my wife and I always eat early supper. And as I looked up on the left side of the carport I saw two Shining Cyliner shape objects flying in and out of a Great Big white and light Gray looking Cloud and all of the Clouds were so low until I sad to my self I could reach up and took it. An at that moment one flying object went inside of the big cloud and the other one went inside of a smaller cloud and nitherone of them came back out of the clouds and I sat there and I wacthed the Clouds passing on by. And I was thinking Damn I just saw two flying objects and my wife would not belive me if I told her. Two Cyliner shape objectwith a Red band half way of the objects.
